Rules:
Coordinate:
You may 'lend' this card to another player on their turn. To do so, set this card aside and draw a card. Until the end of the turn the active player may choose to gain the benifits of this card. Then, at the end of the turn, discard this card.

Vigilant:
At the end of your turn, do not discard this card. Instead, leave it in play in front of you.

Mobilize:
When you buy this card, preform this cards Mobilize effect immediately.

Sacrifice:
You may kill this card to gain its Sacrifice effect.
